query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `image_gallery` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `page_id` int NOT NULL,
  `section_id` int,
  `file_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `file_key` text NOT NULL,
  `url` text NOT NULL,
  `mime_type` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `file_size` int NOT NULL,
  `width` int,
  `height` int,
  `alt_text` text,
  `caption` text,
  `image_type` enum('hero_background','team_photo','office_gallery','logo','favicon','og_image','section_image','custom') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'custom',
  `sort_order` int DEFAULT 0,
  `is_active` boolean DEFAULT true,
  `uploaded_by` int NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `image_gallery_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `page_analytics` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `page_id` int NOT NULL,
  `session_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `visitor_id` varchar(255),
  `ip_address` varchar(45),
  `user_agent` text,
  `referrer` text,
  `utm_source` varchar(255),
  `utm_medium` varchar(255),
  `utm_campaign` varchar(255),
  `utm_term` varchar(255),
  `utm_content` varchar(255),
  `country` varchar(100),
  `city` varchar(100),
  `device_type` enum('desktop','mobile','tablet','unknown') DEFAULT 'unknown',
  `browser` varchar(100),
  `os` varchar(100),
  `time_on_page` int DEFAULT 0,
  `scroll_depth` int DEFAULT 0,
  `did_apply` boolean DEFAULT false,
  `application_id` int,
  `viewed_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `page_analytics_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `analytics_events` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `page_id` int NOT NULL,
  `session_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `event_type` enum('page_view','button_click','form_submit','video_play','video_complete','link_click','scroll_milestone','time_milestone','application_start','application_complete','custom') NOT NULL,
  `event_name` varchar(255),
  `event_data` json,
  `occurred_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `analytics_events_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
